invalid type: string "Experiences on Trvios represent single-day or multi-hour activities curated by local guides. Examples: - Stargazing workshops in high-altitude camps in Spiti and Ladakh. - Traditional Rajasthani cooking classes in Udaipur. - Heritage walking tours in old Delhi and Varanasi. - Scuba diving sessions in South Goa. These can be booked standalone or added to any multiday trip pack